about.summary: Software to calculate molecular descriptors and fingerprints.

name: padel
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "padel" %}
{% set version = "2.21" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: http://www.yapcwsoft.com/dd/padeldescriptor/versions/PaDEL-Descriptor%20v{{ version }}.zip
  sha256: 9cfba80da884d67e79dc9777fbe842f84ee08b5457251eda37e5a2d8cfd80637

build:
  number: 0
  skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
  host:
    - openjdk
    - python >=3
  run:
    - openjdk
    - python >=3

test:
  commands:
    padel -help

about:
  home: http://www.yapcwsoft.com/dd/padeldescriptor/
  license: GNU Affero GPL v3
  license_family: AGPL
  license_file: license/LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Software to calculate molecular descriptors and fingerprints.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - simonbray
